{"id": 2018, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在游戏里都体验过哪些意味深长的虐心时刻？", "description": "坐在锅里攀登险峰，一锄不慎重回起点……这好像和我的人生也没啥两样。（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 1662, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201711171146206mU2EfGcFjO7kQd8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-20T03:00:47Z", "options": [{"id": 249856, "content": "要么花钱氪，要么拿命肝", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147030}, {"id": 249857, "content": "我是大佬 玩游戏不虐心", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187732}, {"id": 249858, "content": "买活虐泉被灭一波反推超级兵被翻盘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808042}, {"id": 253954, "content": "被不明aoe打死/被狂鼠和半藏缘分到/明明路霸打算拉的不是你，但是却被拉过去了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211109}, {"id": 249860, "content": "胜败乃兵家常事 大侠请重新来过", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090312}, {"id": 250116, "content": "晕3D还爱3D，刚涂了护手霜转身都能调个角度，同伴跑的嗖嗖快使劲跟也跟不上，发现自己在努力往地里钻。昨儿和老铁连麦荒野行动，说的最多的就是你在哪？？！！！老铁说，我在这儿，拿枪指着你呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808898}, {"id": 249861, "content": "EQ二连闪现接大操作妥妥的，越塔杀人差一下，自己die", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153949}, {"id": 249862, "content": "打到第二部的最终boss前被告知没有第一部游戏的精灵数据，就无法开启第二部最终boss的关卡？？？玩了几十个小时突然心塞到死……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993360}, {"id": 249863, "content": "快要打boss结果被迷宫传送回入口", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923997}, {"id": 249864, "content": "掘地求生", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713467}, {"id": 249865, "content": "对面:?  ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046188}, {"id": 251658, "content": "玩猎天使魔女时，总看不到贝姐穿什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 204323}, {"id": 249867, "content": "大龙要被干死了！快来抢掉！等等马上红爸爸到手…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188595}, {"id": 249868, "content": "自己伤害不高 但是肉很厚 好不容易快把boss磨死了 突然蓝屏", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187802}, {"id": 249869, "content": "转专业来到新的班级，一起玩丢手绢没有人会丢给你?", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176854}, {"id": 249870, "content": "掘地求升", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532582}, {"id": 249871, "content": "寒鸦号突然飞到了天上，有一次甚至180°翻过来露出了龙骨。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025222}, {"id": 249872, "content": "使命召唤8，肥皂的死与钱队悲痛欲绝\n刺客信条启示录，ezio与已经是枯骨的阿泰尔对话", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628790}, {"id": 249873, "content": "绝地求生1V1决战，被毒死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147952}, {"id": 250642, "content": "Beholder\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191662}, {"id": 249875, "content": "胜利就在眼前。突然一黑?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662330}, {"id": 249876, "content": "快要通关的时候电源插头不小心弄掉，断电", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026536}, {"id": 250132, "content": "很多在你觉得很有希望的时候，往往恰是你最悲催，最命运多舛的时候，因为乐极生悲……（同样适用于现实生活哦）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154871}, {"id": 249877, "content": "不知道哪个方向谁在打我", "image": null, "praise_count": 214, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188644}, {"id": 250646, "content": "游戏三大错觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104122}, {"id": 250137, "content": "酒吞童子什么时候最厉害？\n被混乱的时候最厉害！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1160507}, {"id": 249882, "content": "有两对情侣和我五黑", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155587}, {"id": 